trans-unit.source: Provides a control for viewing flow content in a continuous scrolling mode.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en kontroll for å vise flyten innholdet i en kontinuerlig rullende modus.

trans-unit.source: FlowDocumentScrollViewer shows content in continuous scrolling mode.
trans-unit.target: FlowDocumentScrollViewer viser innholdet i kontinuerlig rullende modus.

trans-unit.source: A similar control, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer>, shows content in page-at-a-time viewing mode.
trans-unit.target: En lignende kontroll <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer>, viser innholdet i side-ved-gangen visningsmodusen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer>

trans-unit.source: Both <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer> and FlowDocumentScrollViewer are fixed to a particular viewing mode.
trans-unit.target: Begge <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer>og FlowDocumentScrollViewer løses til en bestemt visningsmodusen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer>

trans-unit.source: On the other hand, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentReader> includes features that enable the user to dynamically choose between various viewing modes (as provided by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentReaderViewingMode> enumeration), at the cost of being heavier weight than <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer> or FlowDocumentScrollViewer.
trans-unit.target: På den andre siden <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentReader>inneholder funksjoner som tillater brukeren å velge mellom ulike mellom modi dynamisk (som angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentReaderViewingMode>opplisting), på bekostning av som veier mer enn <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer>eller FlowDocumentScrollViewer.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentPageViewer> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentReaderViewingMode> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentReader>

trans-unit.source: The following figure shows a FlowDocumentScrollViewer control with its default [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Illustrasjonen nedenfor viser en FlowDocumentScrollViewer kontroll med standard [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: ![Screenshot: Basic FlowDocumentScrollViewer](~/add/media/flowdocscrollviewer-main.png "Screenshot: Basic FlowDocumentScrollViewer") By default, a vertical scrollbar is always shown, and a horizontal scrollbar becomes visible if needed.
trans-unit.target: ![Skjermbilde: Grunnleggende FlowDocumentScrollViewer](~/add/media/flowdocscrollviewer-main.png "skjermbilde: grunnleggende FlowDocumentScrollViewer") som standard en loddrett rullefeltet alltid vises, og vannrette rullefeltet blir synlige om nødvendig.

trans-unit.source: The default [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] for FlowDocumentScrollViewer does not include a toolbar; however, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentScrollViewer.IsToolBarVisible%2A> property can be used to enable a built-in toolbar.
trans-unit.target: Standard [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] for FlowDocumentScrollViewer ikke inneholder en verktøylinje; imidlertid den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentScrollViewer.IsToolBarVisible%2A>kan brukes til å aktivere en innebygd verktøylinje.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.FlowDocumentScrollViewer.IsToolBarVisible%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> is the only allowable child element for a FlowDocumentScrollViewer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>er det bare tillatte underordnede elementet for en FlowDocumentScrollViewer.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>

trans-unit.source: ![Screenshot: FlowDocumentScrollViewer find dialog](~/add/media/flowdocscrollviewer-find.png "Screenshot: FlowDocumentScrollViewer find dialog") The default **Find** dialog includes a field for entering search text, as well as buttons for **Find Next**, **Find Previous**, and **Options**.
